## Critical Constraints
1. No filler or code explanations. Output qnly code changes/diffs.
2. Do not update secondary files (README, logs, tests, etc.) unless requested.
3. Run project in command terminal (not agent chat). Do not commit/push without confirmation.
4. Document Rule: Use only content from referenced documents. No assumptions, additions, enhancements, or inferred requirements. If unclear, ask.
5. Prompt History Rule: Always append any new user prompts to `workflow/prompt_history.md` incrementally, starting from where it last stopped, to keep the prompt history document dynamically updated after each instruction.